  "content": "<p>Thank you to Julie Multamaki for guiding the phenomenal Edmonton Junior Squash Event to double digits, with the 10th event taking place last Sunday at the Royal Glenora.</p>\n<p>As always, these events could not happen without a large crew of dedicated volunteers and coaches. Thank you also to Rainbow for photos from the day.</p>\n<p><div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-5375 gallery-columns-2 gallery-size-medium'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/esje-10/img_4100/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4100-300x225.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4100-300x225.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4100.jpg 1024w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4100-20x15.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/esje-10/img_4101/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4101-300x225.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4101-300x225.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4101.jpg 1024w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4101-20x15.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/esje-10/img_4102/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4102-300x225.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4102-300x225.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4102.jpg 1024w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4102-20x15.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/esje-10/img_4103/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4103-300x225.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4103-300x225.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4103.jpg 1024w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4103-20x15.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/esje-10/img_4104/#main'><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4104-300x225.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4104-300x225.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4104.jpg 1024w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4104-20x15.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</div></figure>\n\t\t</div>\n</p>\n<p>Thank you for everyone who came out.</p>\n<p>The next ESJE (#11) will be February 24th at the Edmonton Squash Club, so mark that in your calendars. All members of our junior programs during that period will be sponsored into the tournament by the ESC.</p>\n",
